skillType.desc: Reduces effects that prevent damage by {x} when attacking.

skillType.name: Punch
skillType.desc: A random enemy {y} card takes {x} damage.

skillType.name: Sturdy
skillType.desc: Blocks {x} damage when attacked.

skillType.name: Payback
skillType.desc: Deals {x} damage to any card that attacks this, if this card survives.

skillType.name: Cripple
skillType.desc: Reduces attack of a random enemy {y} card by {x} for a turn.

skillType.name: Cripple All
skillType.desc: Reduces attack of all enemy {y} cards by {x} for a turn.

skillType.name: Gas
skillType.desc: Attacked enemy card takes {x} additional damage after each of their turns.

skillType.name: Shield
skillType.desc: Prevent {x} damage dealt to another random {y} card.

skillType.name: Shield All
skillType.desc: Prevent {x} damage dealt to other friendly {y} cards.

skillType.name: Boost
skillType.desc: Card gets +{x} attack whenever you play a combo.

skillType.name: Recover
skillType.desc: Gets +{x} max health whenever you play a combo

skillType.name: Cheer
skillType.desc: Increases attack of another random friendly {y} card by {x} for a turn. Only targets cards that have not attacked this turn.

skillType.name: Cheer All
skillType.desc: Increases attack of all other friendly {y} cards by {x} for a turn. Only targets cards that have not attacked this turn.

skillType.name: Heal
skillType.desc: Restore {x} health to another damaged {y} card.

skillType.name: Heal All
skillType.desc: Restore {x} health to all other friendly damaged {y} cards.

skillType.name: Leech
skillType.desc: Heals self for {x} after dealing attack damage to a card.

skillType.name: Motivate
skillType.desc: {y} cards adjacent to this get extra attack.

skillType.name: Bomb
skillType.desc: Deal {x} damage to {y} enemies adjacent to the one this attacks.

skillType.name: Crazed
skillType.desc: Gain {x} attack after dealing damage

skillType.name: Hijack
skillType.desc: Steals up to {x} attack from each attack increase on the opposing enemy until next turn.

skillType.name: Bodyguard
skillType.desc: Prevent {x} damage from each skill that targets this card and adjacent allies. Uses the highest Bodyguard available.

skillType.name: Give
skillType.desc: Give a random card the {s} skill with {x} value.

skillType.name: Slow
skillType.desc: Card activates after {x} additional turns.

skillType.name: Enlarge
skillType.desc: When played or comboed, permanently gains {x} maximum health for each enemy card.

skillType.name: Bunker
skillType.desc: Prevents {x} damage dealt to itself.

skillType.name: Burn
skillType.desc: Deals {x} damage to an enemy with the most health, then permanently increases damage dealt to them by Burn by {x}. Does not stack.
